      "updated": 1778322433
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0dfd000000000026eb40",
      "text": "[謎解き]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322942,
      "updated": 1778322946
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0e02000000000026eb41",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322946,
      "updated": 1778322946
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c00000000000026eb29",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/79e4a84d39f61e4f60753099f35a2e6b]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322433,
      "updated": 1778322442
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0ee7000000000026eb45",
      "text": "\tネタバレ防止用画像",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778323175,
      "updated": 1778323175
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0e1b000000000026eb42",
      "text": "\thttps://nishio-nazo.vercel.app/1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322972,
      "updated": 1778322972
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c12000000000026eb2c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322450,
      "updated": 1778322452
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c13000000000026eb2d",
      "text": "タイムアタック要素をつけると終わった後の見返しとかがしにくくなることがわかった(苦笑)[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322452,
      "updated": 1778322997
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c41000000000026eb2e",
      "text": "\tタイムアタックに自分も挑戦してみたい人は先にプレイしてからネタバレを見てね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322498,
      "updated": 1778322985
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0e3a000000000026eb44",
      "text": "\tSNSでの拡散もしにくくなるのでこの形式はイマイチだったな〜と思っている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778323003,
      "updated": 1778323014
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0e28000000000026eb43",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322985,
      "updated": 1778322985
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0d8b000000000026eb3d",
      "text": "Nightmare",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322827,
      "updated": 1778322829
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c42000000000026eb2f",
      "text": "[~ [https://gyazo.com/639f56495ffa91f6e77b783076cc439a]]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322498,
      "updated": 1778322533
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0d51000000000026eb3c",
      "text": "\t理屈では(各種記号の意味を正しく推測すれば)これで一意に定まるんだけど、流石に難易度高すぎるだろとおもったのでヒントを追加することにした[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322770,
      "updated": 1778323205
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c5e000000000026eb30",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322527,
      "updated": 1778322527
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0d90000000000026eb3e",
      "text": "Very Hard",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322832,
      "updated": 1778322837
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c78000000000026eb32",
      "text": "[~ [https://gyazo.com/9487ef504f9c52c8af43a19d63901f11]]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322552,
      "updated": 1778322557
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c75000000000026eb31",
      "text": "\t実はこのヒントなしでHardでの追加ヒントだけを足すのの方を先に思いついたのだが、その後どっちが先に出すべきヒントか考えて画面フットプリントの小さいこっちを先にした[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322549,
      "updated": 1778323237
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0dbf000000000026eb3f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322880,
      "updated": 1778322880
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c8f000000000026eb35",
      "text": "[~ [https://gyazo.com/ea474417b1b802414e21df4e088f90d4]]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322576,
      "updated": 1778322579
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c8d000000000026eb34",
      "text": "　これを当初Normalにしようかと思っていたが難しそうなのでヒントを追加することにした[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322573,
      "updated": 1778327583
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff20190000000000b9a554",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778327578,
      "updated": 1778327578
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c94000000000026eb36",
      "text": "[~ [https://gyazo.com/5eab98cdaebabcbbb2995647adbe87a5]]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322581,
      "updated": 1778322602
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff20230000000000b9a555",
      "text": "　追加したヒントの置き場所に苦労している[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778327588,
      "updated": 1778327599
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0c96000000000026eb37",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322583,
      "updated": 1778322601
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0cab000000000026eb39",
      "text": "[~ [https://gyazo.com/bdaf2a638b970a42763b5d151ef9904b]]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322603,
      "updated": 1778322623
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0ca5000000000026eb38",
      "text": "\tここまでやるとGPT Proが回答できるようになった。][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322598,
      "updated": 1778327619
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff0d23000000000026eb3b",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 丸がアルファベットであることをここまでProは気づかなくて、ずっとカタカナを入れようとしていた]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778322723,
      "updated": 1778322749
    },
